<s> The current "Help Wanted" blurb was always intended to only be there for the Beta.  </s>
<s> For production the intent was to either remove it completely or tone it down to one short sentence/link.  </s>
<s> The format of the file is what Config::General uses, and is supposed to be reminiscent of Apache config file syntax.  </s>
<s> Using a homebrew config parser is not an option as far as I'm concerned (BTDT), and since we need  </s>
<s> Config::General for the other config files it makes little sense to have a custom parser for just the verbose messages resource file.  </s>
<s> However, the Config::General syntax is very flexible so it may well be that we can do what you want even within those confines.  </s>
